<section class="page">
  <div class="wrap narrow legal">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="mt-2 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted mb-4"><em>Template — have a qualified attorney review and finalize before launch.</em></p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">What we collect</h3>
    <p class="muted">Account details (email, hashed password), the profile information and photos you provide, and basic usage data needed to operate the service. We do not require your legal name.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">How we use it</h3>
    <p class="muted">To operate the platform, match you with other members, process payments, keep the community safe, and communicate with you about your account.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Your privacy controls</h3>
    <p class="muted">Private photos are never shown without your explicit, per-member permission. You can edit or delete your content, block members, and deactivate your account at any time.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">What we don't do</h3>
    <p class="muted">We do not sell your personal data. We do not display your profile in public search engines (the site is set to no-index).</p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Data requests</h3>
    <p class="muted">To access, export, or delete your data, contact <a href="mailto:<%= brand.supportEmail %>" class="text-gold"><%= brand.supportEmail %></a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>
